    <item>
      <title>英国警告阿萨德倒台可能引发欧洲移民危机</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-09/uk-warns-assad-downfall-could-trigger-european-migration-crisis</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国外交大臣戴维·拉米警告称，巴沙尔·阿萨德在叙利亚的倒台可能引发欧洲新一轮移民危机，英国暂停了对叙利亚庇护申请的决定。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-09/uk-warns-assad-downfall-could-trigger-european-migration-crisis</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 09 Dec 2024 18:05:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加纳前总统获得巨大授权解决通货膨胀问题</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-09/ghana-election-mahama-faces-slew-of-challenges-after-biggest-mandate-in-decades</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加纳选举前总统约翰·马哈马重返他八年前的职位，赋予他强有力的授权来解决这个西非国家沉重的债务负担和高昂的生活成本。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-09/ghana-election-mahama-faces-slew-of-challenges-after-biggest-mandate-in-decades</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 09 Dec 2024 18:03:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>抗议活动爆发 南非通往莫桑比克的主要贸易路线关闭</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-09/key-s-africa-trade-route-to-mozambique-shut-as-protests-flare</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于与选举有关的抗议活动在东南部非洲国家爆发，南非暂停了与莫桑比克主要边境口岸的运营，莫桑比克是主要的煤炭和铬出口枢纽。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-09/key-s-africa-trade-route-to-mozambique-shut-as-protests-flare</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 09 Dec 2024 17:58:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国卫生部长因讽刺工党议员而面临投诉</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-09/uk-health-chief-faces-complaint-over-quip-about-labour-colleague</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国卫生大臣韦斯·斯特里廷被指控对前内阁同事“行为不端”，这是工党政府各派系之间紧张关系公开化的最新案例。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-09/uk-health-chief-faces-complaint-over-quip-about-labour-colleague</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 09 Dec 2024 17:19:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>纽约州州长霍楚尔计划向数百万居民发放 300 美元支票</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-09/ny-s-hochul-floats-sending-300-checks-to-millions-of-residents</link>
      <description><![CDATA[纽约州州长凯西·霍楚尔 (Kathy Hochul) 希望向 860 万纽约人返还约 30 亿美元，以减轻工薪家庭的通货膨胀成本。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-09/ny-s-hochul-floats-sending-300-checks-to-millions-of-residents</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 09 Dec 2024 17:18:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>叙利亚救援人员挖掘以解救刑讯室中的囚犯</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-09/syria-prison-rescuers-dig-to-free-inmates-from-torture-chambers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在叙利亚巴沙尔·阿萨德倒台后拍摄到的令人心碎的画面中，孩子、老人、妇女和男人纷纷冲向大马士革郊区臭名昭著的塞德纳亚监狱的出口——有些人听到自由的消息后，一脸茫然。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-09/syria-prison-rescuers-dig-to-free-inmates-from-torture-chambers</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 09 Dec 2024 17:03:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国与欧盟明年将就重启关系展开正式谈判</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-09/reeves-vows-uk-will-be-ambitious-in-deepening-ties-with-eu</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国和欧盟将于明年就重启关系开始正式谈判，英国财政大臣雷切尔·里夫斯表示，她希望深化与欧盟的经济联系以促进经济增长。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-09/reeves-vows-uk-will-be-ambitious-in-deepening-ties-with-eu</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 09 Dec 2024 15:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泽连斯基警告特朗普和马克龙注意冲突冻结的风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-09/zelenskiy-discussed-frozen-conflict-guarantees-with-trump</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乌克兰总统泽连斯基表示，他在与美国当选总统唐纳德·特朗普和法国总统埃马纽埃尔·马克龙的会谈中提出了与俄罗斯发生冻结冲突的风险，并要求提供安全保障。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-09/zelenskiy-discussed-frozen-conflict-guarantees-with-trump</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 09 Dec 2024 13:51:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>新日铁为赢得美国工人支持做最后努力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-09/nippon-steel-clarifies-spending-pledge-in-effort-to-save-us-deal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新日本制铁公司公布了其在美国钢铁公司旗下美国钢厂的支出计划，这是其为争取工人和政界人士支持收购这家匹兹堡钢铁制造商而做出的最后一项努力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-09/nippon-steel-clarifies-spending-pledge-in-effort-to-save-us-deal</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 09 Dec 2024 13:03:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
